name: SuSHi (Equestria Girls characters)
description:
Hypernet for generating images stylized as Equestria Girls characters.

The neural network can output both SFW and NSFW images.

To activate, it is enough to specify the name of the character, the list is listed below (updated):

  • sunset-shimmer (Sunset Shimmer) (stable result) \\ v1.3

  • sci-twi | twilight-sparkle (Twilight Sparkle) (stable result) \\ add v1.3

  • rainbow-dash (Rainbow Dash) (not a stable result) \\ add v1.3

perhaps other characters (not a stable result) v1.1

We recommend using it in conjunction with the model CounterfietV25

Recommend using prompt:

  • For Twilight Sparkle - "twilight-sparkle, 1girl, solo" or "sci-twi, 1girl, solo"

  • For Rainbow Dash - "rainbow-dash, 1girl, solo"

  • For Sunset Shimmer - "sunset-shimmer, 1girl, solo"

Recommend using this negative prompt:

watermark, text, error, blurry, jpeg artifacts, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, artist name, (worst quality, low quality:1.4), ((bad anatomy)), watermark, signature, text, logo,contact, (((no bangs))), ((extra limbs)),(3d), Six fingers,Low quality fingers,EasyNegative:0.5,monochrome:1.5, shirt, black clothes, happy, bed, naked, bed hand, bed legs, fat

p.s. I do not know why artifacts appear on all characters except Sunset Shimmer
